{"lastModified":1760348089276,"uri":"c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Motor"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nMotor yacht ELENTARI is a 22.25m (72') sporty shape Sunseeker. She was delivered from the shipyard in 2009 and was fully refurbished in 2021. She can accommodate six guests in three cabins plus an onboard crew of three. ELENTARI’s sporty shape offers exciting top-speed cruising. Guests can choose from the sun pads on the foredeck which catch the sun all day or the aft deck dining space where they can enjoy a leisurely al fresco meal. The swim platform is reached from two staircases on either side of the aft deck and offers guests convenient access to the water.","blueprint":{"name":"ELENTARI","images":["/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::05927b50-a039-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f3af2aa0-a038-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f3b03c10-a038-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0594c540-a039-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::0593dae0-a039-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::059365b0-a039-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::05947720-a039-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::vessel::d5cca461-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::150ba9d0-a039-11ee-a7ac-d7be8742705d.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::8344947358::